txt.en: 'The structure is rebuilt and ready to be turned into a library. There are many books and scrolls we can gather from across the cities and towns of the Eastemnet. The more we add to our library, the more our warriors can learn, and the better prepared we will be for whatever battles we find in our futures.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
